協定的談判。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"反而好奇食安公投點樣影響台美貿易談判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/3500387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F7307%2F3500387&d=HyPHtKP0X271k9gPNCCtZ8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=9c9f9438\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/3500387</a><br />\n<br />\n個公投係入定唔入福島食品"},{"pid":"010e037aa9c9d8d930f21cf8660e9a735fc48079","tid":915421,"uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f92db7980f5bbc9f412a9de78d6fe9aaa9c5fd3e","tid":915421,"uid":143407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf92611d482e967c4f43ba69130b33190a4a3332","tid":915421,"uid":29270,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5bc8a70da857e89831ef2ef57a4b0dd79c0201b0","tid":915421,"uid":143407,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:30:15.000Z","msg":"呢個美國智庫講既野根本係本末倒置<br />\n蔡政府就係因為唔承認九二共識<br />\n所以中共先會打壓你經濟同外交<br />\n如果從高雄輸左呢件事民進黨都得唔到啓發<br />\n一路只搞台獨唔發展經濟<br />\n我敢講兩年後總統選舉一定變天"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:43:11.000Z","msg":"高雄輸係因為民進黨治下幾十年經濟一潭死水所以輸<br />\n<br />\n市長選舉邊有咁政治"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"歸咎一潭死水左幾十年，咁點解上屆陳菊得票會有六成八？<br />\n點解係選前比人叫做「躺著選」既陳其邁會輸？<br />\n點解韓國瑜一開始空降落去高雄參選支持度只有十幾%<br />\n但最終勝出？<br />\n韓打住既旗號係「拼經濟，少對抗」所以先打動左高雄人心<br />\n<br />\n我有個朋友係台灣人，佢正正係住係高雄<br />\n所以先知道佢地諗咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"問題係韓國瑜講果一大堆野<br />\n有幾多會做到，定係剩9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5880c9fde4094282479d449adb593f5be5471af4","tid":915421,"uid":143407,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"010e037aa9c9d8d930f21cf8660e9a735fc48079","tid":915421,"uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f92db7980f5bbc9f412a9de78d6fe9aaa9c5fd3e","tid":915421,"uid":143407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":